wikipedia_page.main: Georgia Adderley (born 8 January 2001) is a Scottish female professional squash player. She reached her highest career singles ranking of 100 in November 2019 during the ongoing 2019 PSA World Tour. As of November 2019, she is ranked 100 according to the PSA World rankings.
